.ds ZZ APPLICATION DEVELOPMENT PACKAGE
.TH SQRT 3L
.XE "sqrt()"
.SH NAME
sqrt \- integer square root
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f3
int sqrt (x)
.sp
int x;
\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.I sqrt
function
returns the 32-bit signed integer closest to the square root of
its 32-bit signed argument.
.SH SEE ALSO
norm(3R).
